reviewText: One of the best movies I've seen lately. It's not for everyone but if you been trough something like this you'll totally understand the meaning of it. Amazing Ranbir and Deepika...as always !

I love love love this movie!  It has a beautiful presentation of the important things in life without getting too overbearing.  The heart sensations this film generated were ones that stayed with me long after viewing.  Love the songs and the acting and bright visual styling.  Ranbir Kapoor is my new favorite Bollywood actor.  I'm so starry-eyed!
Best quality, movie was ok tho, but seriously I found a gem with these sellers, fast delivery and amazing quality!
I find so many of Bollywood movies cheesy or lacking.  I actually found Tamasha to have a good story.  I am a big fan of the actors.
